10th amendment visit

00:16:28.816 --> 00:16:31.500
the National Constitution
Center's interactive

00:16:31.500 --> 00:16:33.712
Constitution and Khan Academy's resources

00:16:33.712 --> 00:16:35.953
on US government and politics.

